  "prompt": "How do I know if he is interested in love or lust?",
  "response": "Here are some signs to help differentiate between love and lust:\n\nLove indicators:\n1. Wants to know you deeply\n2. Shows genuine interest in your life\n3. Respects your boundaries\n4. Wants emotional connection\n5. Introduces you to family/friends\n6. Plans future together\n7. Consistent communication\n8. Supports your goals\n9. Cares about your feelings\n\nLust indicators:\n1. Primarily focused on physical attraction\n2. Minimal deep conversation\n3. Mainly interested in physical intimacy\n4. Inconsistent communication\n5. Avoids serious discussions\n6. No interest in long-term commitment\n7. Prioritizes sexual encounters\n8. Limited emotional investment\n9. Doesn't introduce you to friends/family\n\nAdditional tips:\n- Observe his actions, not just words\n- Trust your instincts\n- Take time to know him\n- Communicate openly about expectations\n- Look for consistent behavior over time\n\nRemember, these are general guidelines. Every relationship is unique, and communication is key to understanding each other's intentions.",
